  <title>Fractal Loss Landscapes, Revisited — Field Notes</title>
  <meta name="description" content="A plain‑language exploration of fractal and multifractal geometry in neural‑network loss landscapes: roughness, nested hierarchies, dynamic minima and why stochastic optimisation thrives in the chaos." />
